      "date": "2016-10-26 22:57:39.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 4:\n\n> Chris, I noticed a few patches submitted a week or two ago that\n > don't have reviewers.  If your patches aren't getting reviewed then\n > they aren't going to be landed.  Ideally, you should select\n > reviewers based on who is working on a particular piece of code\n\nNoted. Thanks",
